She possessed an extra princess who was killed by the prince who would become a tyrant.

I tried to die like the original, but the tyrant didn’t kill me…?

He didn’t kill me, so I wanted to live.

However, the atmosphere surrounding the prince and the Duke is somehow strange.

‘Did I live and change the genre of the novel?’>
